  mutate(ypos = cumsum(prop)- 0.5*prop )

pie = pie + scale_fill_manual(values=rainbow(nrow(tamilnadu_data)))
pie = pie + labs(x = NULL, y = NULL, fill = NULL, title = paste("Crime Share across",Code))

ts_pdata <- data.frame(knn_data[,1],knn_data[,3])

set.seed(1234)
# Splitting data into train
# and test data
split <- sample.split(ts_pdata, SplitRatio = 0.7)
train_cl <- subset(ts_pdata, split == "TRUE")
test_cl <- subset(ts_pdata, split == "TRUE")
test_cl
##                            knn_data...1. knn_data...3.
## YEAR                                2001          2003
## ABETMENT.OF.SUICIDE                   60            72
## EXPOSURE.AND.ABANDONMENT             501           483
## INFANTICIDE                          351           252
## MURDER.OF.CHILDREN                  4446          4593
## PROCURATION.OF.MINOR.GILRS           594           522
## RAPE.OF.CHILDREN                    8085         10269
# Feature Scaling
train_scale <- scale(train_cl[, 1:2])
test_scale <- scale(test_cl[, 1:2])
View(test_scale)
# Fitting KNN Model 
# to training dataset
classifier_knn <- knn(train = train_scale,
                      test = test_scale,
                      cl = train_cl$knn_data...1.,
                      k = 2)
